  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">2025</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">年的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">江湖，如果让我用一个字来形容，是「乱」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">2026</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">年，千问</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">APP</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">开了一个好头</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">——</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">用一个字形容，我觉得是「真」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">好像一夜之间，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">突然从</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">会聊天、会写稿、会做</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PPT”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，跳进了我们真实的生活流程里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">25</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">年看多了各式各样的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">demo</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">演示和</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Agent</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">概念，但就在今天的千问发布会上，千问直接打通了淘宝、闪购、高德、飞猪、支付宝这些真实高频应用，让我真的可以在一个</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对话框里，把生活中真切的需要给搞定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把奶茶点了、把机票订了、把旅行规划好了，甚至把签证、公积金、户口这些原本让人头大的事，一句话问清楚、一步点到位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">要知道</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Google</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">才刚刚宣布准备搞</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">购物，准备把沃尔玛接入</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。很显然，在</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">购物、甚至</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">办事上，阿里已经走在了世界前列。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那么，这样的生态整合具体表现到底如何？给大家说说我的体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5655526992287918\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"778\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007040\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=603ba00e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG3vDWoGjEPAwVwicNutdZw2F8jUEOsPKzmtSh2n8a3Jxha6eCry0kCDBVhTmlqOIljjELsVjm56ic9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:50px;\">01.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">当海外还在讨论</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">“AI&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">购物</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">”</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">，千问已经把</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">“</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">对话即下单</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">”</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">跑进现实</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先说一个特别具体、特别日常的场景，点咖啡。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在千问</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">App&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的对话框里，输入一句话：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">太困了，帮我点一杯咖啡。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">千问会先确认你的地址，然后拉起闪购的商品卡片，帮你选符合要求的饮品规格，生成完整订单，最后在对话里直接调起支付。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">要做的事情只有一件：确认并付款。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没有跳转，没有搜索结果页，也没有再让打开一个外卖</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">App</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果把需求说复杂一点，比如</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">帮我点</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">10</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">杯霸王茶姬，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">20</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">杯古茗，适合公司团建，少糖</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，千问会真的像一个能干的行政助理一样，拆解需求、匹配门店、给你三套方案让你选。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个小小的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点奶茶</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的动作，放去年，真的没有一个</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Agent</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">能做好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前更多是外挂插件，或者</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">跳转到某某</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">App&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">帮你完成</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的工作流逻辑，端到端的实现程度很低。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">这次的千问，是一个</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">AI&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">原生掌控任务、原生执行支付的完整闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最接近的还是</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Google Gemini&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接上沃尔玛，也是在探索这一点：当用户的意图在对话里被表达清楚，交易本身是否还需要</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">平台跳转</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">区别在于，海外的支付链路和账号闭环，在移动端还是有很多卡点；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">千问这次，完成度不像是新产品，已经把淘宝、闪购、支付宝这些已经极其复杂、极其成熟的系统，硬生生揉进了一个</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对话体验里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我想点一份海鲜炒饭，还能给我自动计算最大优惠、把各种能领的红包都用上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007041\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3878a62a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG3vDWoGjEPAwVwicNutdZw2FlW9QFYalSHNM52H9uL4udvwPgztvJbNMVDQiaibBicaoibDMvLCBlMXIicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我对比了一下，因为叠加了千问红包，比我自己原本开会员点的，还便宜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">关键是省心，省时间，几秒钟，动动嘴动动手指就搞定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">26</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">年的核心问题，一个是模型能力的问题，另一个就是系统工程和端侧实现的问题。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">前者</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型的能力够强；后者要求</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不只是</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">理解你说了什么</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，还能真正对接库存、地址、价格、支付、履约这些最脏、最复杂的现实世界变量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">能做到这一步，本身就是世界级的能力壁垒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:50px;\">02.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">一句话点奶茶之外，</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">AI&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">开始真正接管</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">“</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">生活型任务</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">”</span></span></b><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">的执行权</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">如果说点奶茶只是一个足够直观的入口，那真正让我觉得千问方向对了的，是它在</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">任务助理</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">模式里，对复杂生活任务的处理方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.175925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007042\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ede32a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG3vDWoGjEPAwVwicNutdZw2FeFhfeQTia3DGic1WXpIZYLTlnLMwxXm3wsVcicGW8hYdUPsQicsh9CQStw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如旅行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你在千问里输入一句话：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">帮我制定一份南京两日游的旅游规划，预算</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2000</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，想轻松一点。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">千问不会给你一篇泛泛而谈的攻略，而是会自动调用高德来做路线规划，用飞猪来匹配机票、酒店和景区门票，用真实的地理和时间约束，把行程拆成每天可执行的路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点开路线，可以直接导航、直接打车；你看到酒店和景点，可以直接跳转预订。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更有意思的是，这份规划不是静态文本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以继续在对话里修改：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第二天不想太累</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">换一家性价比高一点的酒店</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们是带父母一起出行</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，千问会重新调整整个方案，而不是让你从头再来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://agent.qianwen.com/mos/84b654e8af3d4660939b1e78c9156b68/05e8b7562ab1deb884ba58c98894adbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://agent.qianwen.com/mos/84b654e8af3d4660939b1e78c9156b68/05e8b7562ab1deb884ba58c98894adbe</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">真正意义上，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">不再只是</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">帮你想</span></span><spa